        {"id": "e5", "q": "Choose the correct passive: 'The letter ___ yesterday.'", "o": ["sent", "was sent", "is sent", "has sent"], "a": 1, "e": "Пассивный залог, прошедшее время: was/were + V3. The letter was sent.", "t": "Grammar: Passive Voice", "d": 2},
