        {"id": "e13", "q": "Correct preposition: 'We arrived ___ the airport at 5.'", "o": ["to", "in", "at", "on"], "a": 2, "e": "Arrive AT (конкретное место). Arrive IN (город/страна).", "t": "Grammar: Prepositions", "d": 2},
